{"id": 1661, "genre": 1001, "title": "有关还没到or已经到来的三十岁生活，你有哪些感受？", "description": "“三十岁应该就老了吧”“哦天哪我都快三十岁了是时候好好整理一下我的生活了”“三十岁也就这样啊……”（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 3675, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170502144813WDImpxea9cMK8XNt.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-05T03:00:31Z", "options": [{"id": 200704, "content": "40整的我一笑而过……", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229827}, {"id": 201728, "content": "30啊 和那几个智障在为自己的公司打拼 一定要好好的啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971649}, {"id": 200705, "content": "30岁会与女朋友在家新装修的房子里，玩着PS4，听着Jazz ，养一只狗。谁输了中午饭谁做。然后一起去逛街晚上看看星星睡觉过去。 普通的一个周末 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 133, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 57964}, {"id": 200961, "content": "希望到三十岁 不会后悔这八年的任何决定 更有勇敢", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1019352}, {"id": 200706, "content": "越来越想放慢脚步，看看书，做做饭，学点技能，等待更好的机会", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013245}, {"id": 200962, "content": "浪到30再结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994100}, {"id": 201218, "content": "希望三十岁...算了太远 希望二十岁能在伦敦学设计 有一个帅气的外国男友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997361}, {"id": 200963, "content": "人生有多长！\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024006}, {"id": 201987, "content": "网络时代?只需一部手机?就多一份收入，多一份任性?微信咨询2227887341?每天至少50-300+，上不封顶，半月轻松入2000+?你不比别人差❗️差别就在于你缺少一个有实力的团队和一颗赚钱的心❤️", "image": "img/option/option/201705090809095mU2FYaO6Ap0QNlX.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1027056}, {"id": 200708, "content": "二十岁时打算做的事情，快三十了发现还没做", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772745}, {"id": 201220, "content": "路过烤冷面烤鱿鱼手抓饼～我就发现了年龄差……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024737}, {"id": 200709, "content": "日子还不是一样过", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886824}, {"id": 200965, "content": "30岁还蛮远的，希望到时候还是和哥哥一起，还是每天会因为猫咪不听话吵架，有个宝宝忙忙碌碌平平静静柴米油盐", "image": "img/option/option/20170505194144VHIS8Nnpltk63PQe.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024004}, {"id": 201477, "content": "92年的，感觉自己有30危机了，天天想的多、怕的多、压力大，怎么努力都感觉时间不够用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 542187}, {"id": 209925, "content": "十八岁的我觉得我已经老了....", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1048236}, {"id": 200966, "content": "想着三十岁的我要是一个从容，理智而且能想给妈妈买什么就买什么的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 909687}, {"id": 201478, "content": "希望早日脱单 30岁前有自己的孩子 不过已经老了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760609}, {"id": 201734, "content": "和女朋友有很好的生活在一起。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026439}, {"id": 202502, "content": "宝宝感觉很扎Zn\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014928}, {"id": 200711, "content": "该结婚了", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919562}, {"id": 200967, "content": "我为什么还没有结婚 卧槽", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1019967}, {"id": 201223, "content": "总感觉30依旧没有男票???", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 985087}, {"id": 200712, "content": "感觉时间根本不够用...但是还是懒懒的...", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017722}, {"id": 201224, "content": "健康。有钱。其他不指望了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713736}, {"id": 200713, "content": "此时，27岁的我，\n对30岁满怀期待。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023675}, {"id": 201225, "content": "三十而立的节奏 但是现在生不出孩子 烦恼", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024753}, {"id": 206857, "content": "宝宝不知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908163}, {"id": 200714, "content": "快点离开介个闹心糟心的人世吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 794727}, {"id": 200715, "content": "希望30岁能有个健康的身心", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913331}, {"id": 201227, "content": "32岁\n可惜我结婚了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024763}, {"id": 200716, "content": "有自己的事业，满意的收入，父母健康，有人陪在身边", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916995}, {"id": 200972, "content": "我是不是穿越了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529596}, {"id": 203276, "content": "结婚生孩人生就完了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017263}, {"id": 200717, "content": "居然就快四十了", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807000}, {"id": 201229, "content": "对于学医的来说，30岁刚参加工作而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889832}, {"id": 201485, "content": "想做的事情很多，比读书的时候更加热爱读书，哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1025711}, {"id": 200718, "content": "31了，但是心态还停留在20岁，也不知道是好事还是坏事", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 661172}, {"id": 200974, "content": "三十有几却自觉认为年芳二八", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770274}, {"id": 201230, "content": "如果内心强大到可以战胜失败", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024768}, {"id": 200719, "content": "幻想下，三十岁的他在我们开的sunshiny店里教三十岁的我做慕斯蛋糕旁边可能会有一个学会打酱油的娃。我猜娃会很胖～娃也叫太阳", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988359}, {"id": 200975, "content": "三十而惑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986031}, {"id": 201231, "content": "好吧，我进入了30代了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999533}, {"id": 201487, "content": "开始注重健康，不再日夜颠倒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602900}, {"id": 200976, "content": "开始注重养生了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972358}, {"id": 201232, "content": "三十岁的我博士毕业一年，当住院医师，没钱没房没车，我以前设想的一切未来都不会实现，都比不过当下的艰难～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 582118}, {"id": 200721, "content": "到了三十还能有今天的自在", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 990125}, {"id": 200977, "content": "今天还回忆了下以前的荒唐事", "image": "img/option/option/20170505195403wn5CNqkgrpTude3P.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024013}, {"id": 201489, "content": "爱的人爱我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999503}, {"id": 200978, "content": "报年龄都不说岁数，说出生年份", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972358}, {"id": 201234, "content": "稳定下来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024799}]}